 Food Haus&rsquo;s features a perfect fit for all types of restaurants, bars, caffes &amp;amp;amp; taverns. &amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;  &amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;https://themeforest.net/item/food-haus-restaurant-wordpress-theme/full_screen_preview/19441479&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;img src=&amp;quot;https://d1a6a9r46cnyll.cloudfront.net/c81cb323b086901b7f548be84ab2a96e2559284f/687474703a2f2f666f6f642d686175732e626f6c642d7468656d65732e636f6d2f6c616e64696e672f76342f5468656d652d496e666f5f332e706e67&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;  &amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Since it&rsquo;s a restaurant, bar, caffe &amp;amp;amp; tavern WordPress theme, Food Haus is tailored for serving food and drink business like bar, cafeteria, coffee shop, diner, dining room, inn, saloon, canteen, chophouse, eatery, grill, lunchroom, pizzeria, caf&eacute;, doughtnut shop, eating house, eating place, luncheonette or night club you will find Food Haus packed with carefully selected and crafted features.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;  &amp;lt;p&amp;gt;Food Haus comes with ready to use demo content. With one click import you can get your website ready in minutes. It comes with free updates and free support by our highly acclaimed team.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;  &amp;lt;p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;http://documentation.bold-themes.com/food-haus&amp;quot; rel=&amp;quot;nofollow&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;img src=&amp;quot;https://d1a6a9r46cnyll.cloudfront.net/4cd097988cac6ab8a26bbf7b4d7c08af97503939/687474703a2f2f666f6f642d686175732e626f6c642d7468656d65732e636f6d2f6c616e64696e672f76342f5468656d652d496e666f5f342e706e67&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&amp;lt;a href=&amp;quot;https://boldthemes.ticksy.com/articles/100007543&amp;quot; rel=&amp;quot;nofollow&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;img src=&amp;quot;https://d1a6a9r46cnyll.cloudfront.net/3c747564fa1742cc5a502bed5aa5e555f9bb7381/687474703a2f2f666f6f642d686175732e626f6c642d7468656d65732e636f6d2f6c616e64696e672f76342f5468656d652d496e666f5f352e706e67&amp;qu